node.text:
Trying to keep the front wheel down on this @honda_racing_us rocket isn’t easy 😀
@swapmotolivedotcom put together a video of my first day testing SoCal.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Chase Sexton on August 14, 2021 tagging @monsterenergy, @oakley, and @honda_racing_us. May be an image of dirt bike, motorcycle and outdoors.

node.text:
P5 overall today.
That first Moto crash definitely put me behind the 8ball right away but happy with how we battled back with a holeshot and a much better 2nd Moto. Hungry for more definitely, and looking forward to improving the bike and myself this week! Thanks team ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chase Sexton in Spring Creek Motocross Park with @monsterenergy, @oakley, @alpinestarsmx, and @honda_racing_us. May be an image of dirt bike, motorcycle and text.

node.text:
P4 Overall today at Spring Creek! Fought back well in Moto 1 and had a better Moto 2 fighting my way up to 3rd. I’m just happy to ride more like myself today and get to where I need to be this next half of the season. #SpringCreekMx
Also, I had zero intention of getting that close to cooper and by no means did I mean to make contact with him and was glad he was okay.

node.text: It was a rough day in the office for me this weekend but it just fuels the fire. See you at Spring Creek!
